5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

frame-manager

Generic function

Summary

Returns the frame manager for the specified object.

Signature

frame-manager object => value

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

value
An instance of type false-or
(<frame-manager>).

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the frame manager used to control the look and feel of the display of object.
